.\" Man page for lmm mod
.TH LMM-MOD 1 "2026-01-29" "lmm" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lmm mod \- Enable, disable, or configure installed mods; show mod details
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lmm mod
\fICOMMAND\fR \fIMOD_ID\fR [\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.PP
.B lmm mod show
\fIMOD_ID\fR [\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.PP
.B lmm mod files
\fIMOD_ID\fR [\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Manage installed mods: enable/disable deployment, set update policy, view mod
details (name, description, image, version), or list deployed files.
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
.B enable \fIMOD_ID\fR
Enable a disabled mod (include in deploy).
.TP
.B disable \fIMOD_ID\fR
Disable a mod (keep in cache, exclude from deploy).
.TP
.B set-update \fIMOD_ID\fR \fB--auto\fR|\fB--notify\fR|\fB--pin\fR
Set update policy: auto (apply when checking), notify (show only), pin (ignore updates).
.TP
.B show \fIMOD_ID\fR
Show mod details: name, author, version, summary, description, image URL. Use \fB--json\fR for scriptable output.
.TP
.B files \fIMOD_ID\fR
List files deployed by the mod in the game directory.
.SH OPTIONS (global)
.TP
.BR \-g ", " \-\-game\fR=ID
Game ID (required unless default is set).
.TP
.BR \-p ", " \-\-profile\fR=NAME
Profile (default: default).
.TP
.B \-\-json
For \fBmod show\fR only: output in JSON.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lmm (1),
.BR lmm-list (1),
.BR lmm-update (1),
.BR lmm-deploy (1).
